  <title>Rigid-Body</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Rigid-Body</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rigid-Body</text> is a kinematic name for a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rigid-Body /</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> :</para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">is infinitely stiff - it does not stretch, bend, or twist</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">does not expand with heat</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">is an exact size - no need for a size tolerance</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">does not vibrate</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">does not wear</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Popup Box">Other names are: </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Link, Solid-Body, bar</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> (especially with </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">four-bar&apos;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> )</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
